name: One Night At Stinky's
description:
Welcome to Stinky's maze, you are an orangutan who has been captured by Stinky, you need to collect keys, open doors, run from Stinky, and escape this death game.

Also yes, I know what the title is, but please don't mistake this for a fnaf fangame, it does have some fnaf-y elements to it, but it is NOT a fnaf fangame.
